Module com.fy916.bubblebobble
Package com.fy916.bubblebobble.gaming.elements.features.collision

Interface Collision

All Known Implementing Classes:
CollisionBubble, CollisionCeilingUnit, CollisionEnemy, CollisionFloorUnit, CollisionFruit, CollisionHero, CollisionProjectile, CollisionScoreIndicator, CollisionWallUnit
public interface Collision
An Interface which offers the colliding methods framework, since the objects in the game world all can collide with each other.
This shows the STRATEGY and TEMPLATE Design Pattern.
Author:
fy916
